Speaking on ABC News’ ‘This Week,’ Rep. Boehner said: ‘Rob’s a great friend and a long-time ally.’

He went on to explain in the exclusive interview: ‘(But) I believe that marriage is the union of one man and one woman… It’s what I grew up with. It’s what I believe. It’s what my church teaches me.

‘And I can’t imagine that position would ever change.’

